						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying near the Śiva temple.</p>						

						<p>Hariyaṇṇa Oḍeya, A.D. 1381.</p>						

						<p>Dated Śaka 1303, <hi rend="italic">Durmati, Pushya</hi> śu. 1, Tuesday, corresponding to A.D. 1381, December 17.</p>						

						<p>Registers a gift of land in Mēḍikuru situated in Penugoṇḍa-Mārjavāḍi by the chief to Ōbaḷanātha.</p>						

